03:18.132 --> 03:19.798
♪ Let's go! ♪

03:21.201 --> 03:23.202
♪ Things are looking up ♪

03:23.204 --> 03:25.337
♪ I'm ready for tonight ♪

03:25.339 --> 03:27.839
♪ I feel good, real good ♪

03:27.841 --> 03:30.676
♪ Can't nobody hold me down ♪

03:30.678 --> 03:32.811
♪ I'm gonna take advantage of ♪

03:32.813 --> 03:35.214
♪ All these flashing lights ♪

03:35.216 --> 03:38.183
♪ 'Cause it's the best time,
the best time for it... ♪

03:38.185 --> 03:39.518
♪ We can do it ♪

03:39.520 --> 03:41.019
