♪ Tell me,
what are we waiting for? ♪

03:53.934 --> 03:56.034
♪ Oh, what the hell are
we waiting for? ♪

03:56.036 --> 03:58.036
(sighs)

03:58.038 --> 03:59.805
Look at 'em.

04:01.341 --> 04:02.741
Your brothers are
showing off again.

04:02.743 --> 04:04.676
That's what
