Let's go find Dad.

04:21.862 --> 04:25.530
♪ Gotta believe in yourself
and gotta know your worth ♪

04:25.532 --> 04:28.267
♪ I did it clean as a whistle,
stayed away from dirt ♪

04:28.269 --> 04:29.468
♪ Ah, I told you I'mma get it ♪

04:29.470 --> 04:30.636
♪ Everybody, they talkin' ♪

04:30.638 --> 04:32.137
♪ I dreamt about
how I'm livin' ♪

